---
// about.astro
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="About | Cosmic Astro">
  <article class="about-page">
    <h1>About Cosmic Astro</h1>
    <p>Welcome to Cosmic Astro, a space-themed blog dedicated to exploring the wonders of the universe and sharing insights on building modern static websites with Astro. Our mission is to blend the beauty of outer space with the art of web development.</p>
    <p>Cosmic Astro was created by a passionate developer and space enthusiast who believes that the universe is as much a canvas for creativity as it is for science. Here you'll find articles about galaxies, nebulae, black holes, and tutorials on building static sites with Astro.</p>
    <p>Thank you for joining us on this cosmic journey!</p>
  </article>
</Layout>

<style>
  .about-page {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 2rem auto;
    padding: 2rem;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    border-radius: 8px;
    color: var(--text-color);
  }
  .about-page h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .about-page p {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
</style>
